Megatron to Build Electricals Factory in Cameroon, Tribune Says

-- B y   P i u s   L u k o n g
-- 
2011-08-01T12:12:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-01/megatron-to-build-electricals-factory-in-cameroon-tribune-says.html
South Africa ’s  Megatron Federal  plans
to build a factory to make electrical equipment in  Cameroon ’s
port city of Douala, the Cameroon Tribune reported, citing
Executive Director Ryan Otto.  The plant will make products including electricity meters,
transformers, generators and solar-energy equipment, the
newspaper reported. The locally made goods may lower costs for
consumers, the Tribune cited Dudley Achu Sama, technical adviser
at the ministry of energy and water resources, as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Pius Lukong in Yaounde via Accra at 
 ebowers1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at   asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 